summary: I am utterly fascinated by folktales and myths, so therefore I study comparative mythology and folkloristics from the past and nowadays. I approach these subjects through structuralism, cognitive theory, and the study of languages. There are no cultural areas off-limits to this fascination, and the longing to uncover more worlds motivates me
